<dd>>>Right side of the road</dd>
<dd>>>center of the road</dd>
            </dl>

<p>14)If a vehicle is parked on the side of a road at night</p>
        <dl>
<dd>>>The vehicle should be locked</dd>
<dd>>>Park light should remain on</dd>
<dd><b>>>All of the above</b></dd>
            </dl>
  
<p>15)Fog lamps should be used when</p>
        <dl>
<dd><b>>>There is mist</b></dd>
<dd>>>At night</dd>
<dd>>>When the vehicle opposite is not using the dim light</dd>
    </dl>
<p>16)Zebra lines are meant for</p>
        <dl>
<dd><b>>>Crossing of pedestrians</b></dd>
<dd>>>Stopping vehicles</dd>
<dd>>>Overtaking</dd>
</dl>
<p>17)If an ambulance is approaching</p>
